description: Disassociates a backup gateway from the specified server. After the disassociation process finishes, the gateway can no longer access the virtual machines on the server.

parameters.name: GatewayArn
parameters.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the gateway to disassociate.

nested_items.name: GatewayArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the gateway you disassociated.
